\c 21
\s UPawuli eKesariya
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi sisuka ngomkhumbi sesehlukene labo, sahamba ngendlela eqondileyo\x + 16.11.\x* safika eKosi, lango\add suku\add* olulandelayo eRodesi, sasuka lapho \add saya\add* ePathara;
\v 2 sasesithola lapho umkhumbi ochaphela eFenekiya\x + 11.19.\x*, sangena sahamba ngomkhumbi.
\v 3 Kwathi sesiqhamuka eKuprosi\x + 21.16. 4.36. 27.4,5.\x*, sasesiyitshiyela ngakwesokhohlo, saya ngomkhumbi eSiriya\x + 18.18.\x*, sehlikela eTire\x + 21.7. Mat. 15.21.\x*; ngoba umkhumbi wawuzakwethulela khona impahla\x + 21.2.\x*.
\v 4 Sesibatholile abafundi\x + 20.1,7. 20.30.\x*, sahlala khona insuku eziyisikhombisa; bona bamtshela uPawuli ngoMoya\x + 20.23. 21.11.\x*, ukuthi angenyukeli eJerusalema\x + 21.12,15. Luka 2.4.\x*.
\v 5 Kwathi sekwenzakele ukuthi siqede insuku, sasuka sahamba, bonke basiphelekezela kanye labomkabo labantwana kwaze kwaba ngaphandle komuzi\x + 15.3.\x*; njalo saguqa ngamadolo ekhunjini sakhuleka\x + 7.60.\x*,
\v 6 sesivalelisene, sangena emkhunjini\x + 20.1.\x*, kodwa bona babuyela kibo\x + Joha. 16.32.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Kodwa thina, sesiqedile uhambo ngomkhumbi sisuka eTire\x + 21.7. Mat. 15.21.\x*, safika ePetolemayi\x + Hlu. 1.31.\x*, sesibingelele abazalwane\x + 21.17. Joha. 21.23.\x* sahlala labo usuku lwaba lunye.
\v 8 Kusisa thina esasiloPawuli sasuka\x + 13.13.\x* safika eKesariya\x + 21.16. 8.40.\x*; sesingene endlini kaFiliphu\x + 6.5.\x* umvangeli\x + Efe. 4.11. 2 Tim. 4.5.\x*, owayengomu\add nye\add* wabayisikhombisa\x + 6.5.\x*, sahlala laye.
\v 9 Yena-ke wayelamadodakazi amane, intombi, eziprofethayo\x + 19.6.\x*.
\v 10 Kwathi sesihlezi insuku ezinengi, kwehla umprofethi othile\x + 11.27.\x* uAgabusi ngebizo evela eJudiya\x + 11.28.\x*,
\v 11 wasefika kithi, wathatha uzwezwe lukaPawuli\x + Jer. 13.1-9. 1 Kho. 22.11.\x*, wazibopha izandla kanye lenyawo esithi: Utsho lokho uMoya oyiNgcwele\x + 20.23. 21.33.\x*: Indoda olungolwayo loluzwezwe, amaJuda eJerusalema azayibopha kanje, njalo a\add yi\add*nikele ezandleni zabezizwe.
\v 12 Sesizizwile lezizinto, samncenga thina kanye lalabo ababelapho, ukuthi angenyukeli eJerusalema\x + 21.15. 18.22.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa uPawuli waphendula \add esithi\add*: Lenzani likhala lidabula inhliziyo yami? Ngoba mina sengilungele, kungeyisikho ukubotshwa kuphela, kodwa lokufa eJerusalema ngenxa yebizo leNkosi uJesu\x + 20.24.\x*.
\v 14 Kwathi engancengeki, sathula sathi: Kayenziwe intando yeNkosi\x + Mat. 6.10. Ruthe 1.18.\x*.
\s UPawuli eJerusalema
\p
\v 15 Emva kwalezinsuku sasesilungiselela\x + Hlu. 18.21.\x*, senyukela eJerusalema\x + 21.15. 18.22.\x*.
\v 16 L\add abathile\add* babafundi\x + 11.26.\x* beKesariya\x + 21.8.\x* basebehamba lathi, babuya lothile uMnasoni umKuprosi\x + 21.3.\x*, umfundi omdala\x + 11.26.\x*, ebesizangenisa kuye.
\v 17 Njalo sesifikile eJerusalema, abazalwane\x + 21.7.\x* basemukela ngokuthokoza\x + 15.4.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Kusisa uPawuli wangena lathi kuJakobe\x + 12.17.\x*, labadala bonke babekhona\x + 11.30.\x*.
\v 19 Kwathi esebabingelele, walandisa ngakunye ngakunye\x + 15.12. Roma 15.18,19.\x* izinto uNkulunkulu azenzileyo phakathi kwabezizwe ngenkonzo yakhe\x + 1.17.\x*.
\v 20 Kwathi sebe\add ku\add*zwile, bayidumisa iNkosi\x + 4.21. 11.18. Mat. 15.31.\x*; bathi kuye: Uyabona, mzalwane, ukuthi zinengi kangakanani izigidi zamaJuda akholwayo; futhi bonke batshisekela umlayo\x + Gal. 1.14. Seb. 22.3. Roma 10.2.\x*;
\v 21 njalo sebetsheliwe ngawe\x + 21.24. Luka 1.4.\x*, ukuthi ufundisa wonke amaJuda aphakathi kwabezizwe ukuthi adele uMozisi, usithi angasoki abantwana, lokuthi angahambi ngamasiko\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 22 Pho-ke kuyini? Isibili kufanele ukuthi ixuku libuthane; ngoba bazakuzwa ukuthi usufikile.
\v 23 Ngakho yenza lokhu esikutsho kuwe; silamadoda amane abalesifungo phezu kwawo\x + Nani 6.2,18. Seb. 18.18.\x*;
\v 24 athathe kanye lawe, uzihlambulule kanye lawo\x + 21.26. 24.18. Joha. 11.55.\x*, njalo uhlawule indleko zawo, ukuze aphuce amakhanda\x + Nani 6.2,18. Seb. 18.18.\x*, njalo ukuze bakwazi bonke ukuthi kakulalutho kulokho abakutshelwe ngawe, kodwa ukuthi lawe uhamba ngokulondoloza umlayo\x + 21.24. Luka 1.4.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa mayelana labezizwe abakholwayo thina sesibhalile, saquma \add sathi\add* bangagcini lutho olunjalo, ngaphandle kokuthi kabazile okuhlatshelwe izithombe, legazi, lokukhanyiweyo, lokufeba\x + 15.20,29.\x*.
\v 26 UPawuli wasewathatha amadoda, kusisa wahlanjululwa kanye lawo\x + 21.26. 24.18. Joha. 11.55.\x* wangena ethempelini\x + Nani 6.13.\x*, ukubika ukuphela kwensuku zokuhlanjululwa, kwaze kwalethwa umnikelo walowo lalowo\x + Nani 6.10-12.\x* wawo.
\s AmaJuda avusa umsindo; uPawuli uyabotshwa
\p
\v 27 Kwathi sezizaphela insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Nani 6.9.\x*, amaJuda\x + 24.18.\x* avela eAsiya\x + 2.9.\x* ayembonile ethempelini\x + 26.21.\x*\x + 24.18.\x*, avusa ixuku lonke\x + 19.32.\x*, amdumela ngezandla\x + Luka 21.12.\x*,
\v 28 amemeza \add athi\add*: Madoda maIsrayeli, sizani! Nguye lumuntu ofundisa bonke endaweni zonke okuphambene lesizwe, lomlayo\x + 25.8. 6.13. Joha. 11.48.\x*, lalindawo; futhi ungenisile lamaGriki ethempelini, useyingcolisile lindawo engcwele\x + 24.6.\x*.
\v 29 Ngoba ayebonile ngaphambili uTrofimu\x + 20.4.\x* umEfesu\x + 18.19.\x* emzini elaye, amkhumbulela ukuthi uPawuli umngenisile ethempelini.
\v 30 Lomuzi wonke wanyakazela, labantu bagijimela ndawonye, bamdumela uPawuli\x + 26.21. 2 Kho. 11.15.\x* bamhudulela ngaphandle kwethempeli; leminyango yahle yavalwa.
\v 31 Kuthe besafuna ukumbulala, ilizwi lafika enduneni enkulu\x + Joha. 18.12. Mark. 6.21.\x* yesigaba\x + Joha. 18.3.\x*, ukuthi iJerusalema yonke iyaphithizela\x + 19.32.\x*;
\v 32 eyahle yathatha amabutho lezinduna zekhulu, yagijimela kubo\x + 23.27. 24.7.\x*; kwathi sebebona induna enkulu lamabutho, bayekela ukumtshaya uPawuli\x + Joha. 18.12. Mark. 6.21.\x*.
\v 33 Induna enkulu yasisondela\x + Joha. 18.12. Mark. 6.21.\x*, yambamba, yalaya ukuthi \add ka\add*botshwe\x + 20.23. 21.11.\x* ngamaketane amabili\x + 12.6. 22.30. 26.29. 28.20.\x*, yabuza ukuthi ungubani, lokuthi wenzeni.
\v 34 Abanye exukwini bememeza okunye labanye okunye; kodwa ingelakulazi iqiniso ngenxa yomsindo, yalaya ukuthi asiwe enkambeni yamabutho\x + 21.37. 22.24. 23.10,16,32.\x*.
\v 35 Kwathi esefikile ezikhwelweni\x + 21.40. 22.30. 23.10,15.\x*, kwenzeka ukuthi athwalwe ngamabutho ngenxa yokufutheka kwexuku;
\v 36 ngoba ixuku labantu lalandela limemeza \add lisithi\add*: Msuseni\x + 22.22. Luka 23.18. Joha. 19.15.\x*!
