\v 37 Kwathi uPawuli esezangeniswa enkambeni yamabutho\x + 21.37. 22.24. 23.10,16,32.\x* wathi enduneni enkulu\x + Joha. 18.12. Mark. 6.21.\x*: Kuvunyelwe yini ukuthi ngikhulume ulutho kuwe? Yona yasisithi: Uyasazi isiGriki yini?
\v 38 Kanti kawusuye yini lowomGibhithe\x + 5.36,37.\x* okwathi kungakafiki lezinsuku wenza umvukela\x + 17.6.\x*, wakhokhelela enkangala amadoda azinkulungwane ezine angababulali\x + Mat. 24.26.\x*?
\v 39 Kodwa uPawuli wathi: Mina ngingumuntu ongumJuda, weTarsu\x + 22.3. 9.11.\x* yeKilikhiya, isakhamuzi somuzi ongadelelekanga; ngiyakuncenga, ngivumela ngikhulume ebantwini.
